OL,3,CD-Day veterans honour those lost with
OL,4,C'emotional' ferry crossing to Normandy
OL,6,FITV News' reporter Chloe Keedy sets
OL,7,Fsail from Portsmouth, with a group of
OL,8,FD-Day veterans retracing their journey
OL,9,Facross the channel
OL,11,FThe Mont St Michel ferry makes the
OL,12,Fsame crossing every day. But today's
OL,13,Fjourney - from Portsmouth to Normandy
OL,14,Fin France - was a hugely symbolic one.
OL,16,FOn board were more than 30 veterans
OL,17,Fwho made the very same voyage on D-
OL,18,FDay, 80 years ago.
