OL,3,CD-Day veterans honour those lost with
OL,4,C'emotional' ferry crossing to Normandy
OL,6,FIt was a moment that changed not just
OL,7,Ftheir lives, but the course of the
OL,8,FSecond World War.
OL,10,FWhen they set sail on June 6, 1944,
OL,11,Fthey had no idea if they'd ever see
OL,12,Fhome again.
OL,14,FToday, they were given a heroes send
OL,15,Foff. Waving crowds lined the port, a
OL,16,Fpipe band played, and an RAF fly-past
OL,17,Froared overhead.
