OL,3,CD-Day veterans honour those lost with
OL,4,C'emotional' ferry crossing to Normandy
OL,6,F"Every one of those men and women who
OL,7,Ftook part in the Normandy invasion
OL,8,Fmust have gone out there knowing they
OL,9,Fwouldn't come back."
OL,11,FAnd that is why - in their late 90s -
OL,12,Fthese veterans continue to make a
OL,13,Fjourney that must be as exhausting as
OL,14,Fit is emotional.
OL,16,FThis was the final voyage for so many
OL,17,Fof their comrades and, 80 years on,
OL,18,Fthey know this could be the last time
OL,19,Fthey make it too.
